Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个还没发觉自己命运的男人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历经千辛万苦 终于到达了利多纳村的西蒙和卡米那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着他们两人的是 乘着强力GANMEN的兽人维拉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在卡米那面临险境时挺身而出的西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在激烈的战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们所乘坐的GANMEN－Gurren和Lagann合体了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被Gurren-Lagann的钻头打飞了的维拉鲁的GANMEN－ENKI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gurren-Lagann究竟藏着什么样的力量呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.22,0:02:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4话 脸越多越厉害吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兽人的大本营是不是还很远呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?特训?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来吧 西蒙!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体啊 合体!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次实在是太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 西蒙 所谓男人的合体啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是像这样 更美丽 灼热燃烧的灵魂啊~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那确实是..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙! 跳到我的肩膀上来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 真人这么做也没意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 卜塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 回答我!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用哪里合体啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人 看起来玩得挺高兴的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃..是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要调查的是什么来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 看着好了 接下来..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咻咻的~把手套~戴在玉手上~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 大家伙们~要出场了~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然带着这种东西 真是恶趣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 你真失礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼..好 好 加油吧~好好干~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好~加油吧~好好干~好好~好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?果然呢 虽然到现在也算看过许多GANMEN了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还是假想 但如果我所想的没错的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台GANMEN有特殊的..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~抱歉抱歉 一不小心手滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 西蒙!没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉哈 抱歉~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小机机..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow~居然扔中Lagann了 运气真不错~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 西蒙 要继续了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还差一点就好了..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 这不也挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~~合体啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥住手啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙!有什么好逃的 来合体吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合 体 波!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不明白你在说什么啊 会死的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 那帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招 合体波!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦 大哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵呵呵..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 我已经饿得..不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 西蒙!是男人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饿肚子这点小事 用气势打飞它!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?本大人也..肚子饿了..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的少年~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危险啊 不过已经没事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女..女人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够合格吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生..给我站起来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候想要动起来就要用敲的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 去死吧 你这兽人混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥? 你说兽人?开什么玩笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人类?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小事一看不就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?你这家伙算什么东西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在被追杀吗?嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 装人还装得挺像的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不小心点说话真的杀了你哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴 张开看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 没长獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 这家伙的善后工作你打算怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然扔炸弹过来..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善后? 话说为什么人类会坐在GANMEN上?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你这样的家伙连杀的价值都没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANMEN啊 就是只能由兽人来驾驶的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小饼干一样理所当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啊 我强抢过来的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都驾驶过了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这世界地平线的尽头的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从吉哈村钻出来 打败的GANMEN之多犹如繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gurren团 鬼队长就是说的本大人啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺像的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡米那!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡米那大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡米那大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是长得挺不错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帅!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涩涩的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是长女奇悠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..我是次女奇侬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大人是三女奇亚露哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还有哥哥..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇坦!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事! 我们是兽人猎人－黑之兄弟啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用这个燃烧水弹把GANMEN..那个..干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这个黑色的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 很可怕的哦 咚~的一声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑原~桑原~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇悠!奇侬!奇亚露! 你们几个给我退下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙啊 就用我的拳头..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 游戏就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:10:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非由我们几个来负责午餐不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 饿着肚子的男人 什么用场都派不上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子真好啊 能和那样的好男人一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的家伙哪里好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他声音不是挺大的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很强..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚也不丑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睫毛也很长对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 是水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有水的地方就会有生物聚集哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看啊 找到好像很不错的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好好吃啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈..居然说是要去兽人的大本营?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你们这样的菜鸟?在说什么呐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在害怕吧 你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁怕了!只是说别小看兽人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你也是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早上起就追着有16张脸的GANMEN 忙得根本没空吃饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有16张脸?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 哪来的那样的GANMEN啊 别说梦话了~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连16张脸都不知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙啊 肚子饿了就什么都不想干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 看起来很美味的云!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 那块肉云是我的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开!是我先发现的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?要来干一场吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 吵什么呐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊 看起来很好吃的 哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西 能吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没腐烂就能吃的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙!刚才咬了我对吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭说话了..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长 好好看看这群家伙的蠢样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 是人类啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的午睡被打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不管了 吃掉它们!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是些毛球 别太得意了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢小看毛球!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家集合!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 难道说那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 那些家伙很像是兽人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兽人一只都不能放过!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到这附近的兽人 肯定是那个有16张脸的家伙没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群家伙是我们的猎物!YA~HO!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登场啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶..西蒙!我们Gurren团也要上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 使不出力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点 可恶..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜鸟就乖乖退下吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 西蒙!用Gurren-Lagann一口气干掉它们!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么!为什么他们能开动GANMEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 西蒙 合体吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ＯＫ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 你干什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰唆! 你的那些特训成果到哪儿去了 西蒙!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去 会被干掉啊 不快点合体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才两台就想合体?那就给你们看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是真正的合体!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16面合体!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人吃惊啊 居然还有其他能合体的GANMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANMEN不就是那种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋! 那种东西怎么能叫合体!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓合体啊 是更高级..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会被干掉的..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙!听好 所谓男人的合体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美丽灼热燃烧的灵魂啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么多废话 快点合体不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 Gurren-Lagann的合体的级数根本不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 卜塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大哥为什么要这么做..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 大哥 我明白了 大哥~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小不点..没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 大哥 已经撑不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙!跑起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙!跑啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小不点开始跑了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔出去 快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 张开弹幕了啊 你挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16张脸的家伙们就慢慢着急去吧 哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:16:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 大哥教给我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 跟大哥扔的石头比起来 这些算得上什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的合体 那就是气势!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是飞翔于天际之美!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:18:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟合体 Gurren-Lagann!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下胜负已定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gurren..Lagann?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帅啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16面合体!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很大..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 只是傻大个儿木偶机器人罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇坦!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 奇悠 奇侬 奇亚露!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生..畜生..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 使不出力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了 食物什么的上那儿找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜塔?是说吃了这尾巴?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 西蒙 连钻头都开始觉得好像很好吃了..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥!把这个吞进胃里!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说脸越多就越厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的合体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是像廉价的恋爱一样 一会儿分又一会儿合的东西啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西不是真正的羁绊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是徒有其表的假货罢了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的羁绊吗..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 就是那点不同!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的合体啊 完全没理解这个真谛啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 手上 手上的钻头!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来让你们明白吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(也可作 把你们串起来吧!解)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1只 !2只! 3只! 4只! 5只!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢坏我事!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16只!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下你们明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的Gurren-Lagann..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撤了!我们还会再来的 给我记着!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了!不愧是卡米那大人..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台GANMEN真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 你们都还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 真是危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点就送命了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?怎么了 哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为啊 我还以为你们..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还没那么脆弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 去卡米那那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡米那大人~好厉害~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下又要通宵修理了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 毛多死郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说屁股上长毛的家伙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想再干一架吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想当黑之兄弟的话 随便怎么来都行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 是没人会把你当大人看的老么哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙才是 想进我们男人的象征Gurren团的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便什么时候来打声招呼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BYE BYE~darling~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衷心祝福我们能再见 卡米那大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家 下次在哪儿再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..话说刚才的那个真是好吃啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 站起来!让我吃那个!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.89,0:22:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜塔也想吃吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西蒙~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 绝对不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 西蒙 西蒙 来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.85,0:22:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算脑袋里再怎么明白 要用身体去明白
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算身体自说自话的先动了 脑袋里却想着别的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.67,0:24:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说只有那个是!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.88,0:24:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 天元突破Gurren-Lagann
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不明白啊!